Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.85,0:00:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Spike. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just, uh, wanted to\Nmake sure you're ready
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,for your big\Nceremony today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. Wow, I still can't\Nbelieve my friends and I
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,are getting medals of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding? You\Ntotally deserve it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you saved Equestria\Nfrom Queen Chrysalis
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with the help of Trixie\Nand Thorax and Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah. I know what\Nhappened. I was kinda there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.66,0:00:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Uh, so\Nwhat are you wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not sure. Why? Am I\Nsupposed to dress up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I mean, you could. It's\Nlike Rarity always says:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"There's no such thing\Nas overdressed darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.45,0:00:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just the best-looking\Npony in the room!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you\Nlooking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuz there was a spider there\Nbut it's gone now so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Starlight!\NBye!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh. She had no idea.\NWe're a good team, Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparkle? Yeah we are.\NSo, do you think she'll like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want this present to\Nsay "I'm so proud of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.32,0:01:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,both as a mentor\Nand a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.74,0:01:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestria is safer\Nthanks to you."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I thought you were getting\Nher a mirror, like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should\Nget her a card,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.92,0:01:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,cause I don't think the\Nmirror will say all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think\Nshe'll like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just what\Nher room needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing she'll see\Nwhen she wakes up is herself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,surrounded by all her friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I plan on giving it to\Nher after the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you need to get the castle\Nready for the celebration?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah. Pinkie Pie's\Ngot that covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:01:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles\NBy YayPonies\NHey look! it's NEW PONY SEASON TIME!\Nhttps://yp1.yayponies.eu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight, Trixie,\NThorax and Discord
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,were brave in the\Nface of danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,resourceful when\Nthings got challenging
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and proved that the\Nbonds of friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how unlikely, are\Nstronger than any adversity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,By stopping\NQueen Chrysalis,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:02:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,not only did they\Nsave Equestria,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,they set the changelings\Nfree from her reign.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Discord! Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why we're proud\Nand honored to give them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the Equestrian Pink\NHearts of Courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Oh! Not quite!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! There it is.\NYAAAAAAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We are so proud of you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the Great and\NPowerful Trixie's pleasure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to save you from\Nyour imminent doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Because you did\Nit all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you managed\Nto do it without magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's ever stood up\Nto Chrysalis like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just did what\Nanypony would've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful\Nfeeling, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching your\Nstudent shine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the way you always\Nknew they could.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My cheeks are sore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I've ever\Nsmiled this much in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only imagine\Nwhat that feels like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Starlight is student\Nof the year, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She has so much\Npotential.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what are we going\Nto do with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And by "we" I\Ndefinitely mean you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Being her mentor\Nand all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,her destiny falls\Nsquarely on your haunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've planned enough\Nfriendship lessons
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to cover the next\Nthree years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly Starlight is beyond\Nbasic friendship lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.67,0:05:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She just won a medal,\Nfor Equestria's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were joking.\NYou are joking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously you should have a\Ngrand master plan for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the same way Celestia\Nset you on a path
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that eventually\Nmade you a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good. I'm sure she can't\Nwait to hear all about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So how's the whole\Nruling-a-kingdom thing going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit... overwhelming.\NBut we're adjusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't have friendship\Nwithout makeovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Starlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight has something\Nvery important to tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:06:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just you really, but\NI'm nosey and I want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Would you\Nexcuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Twilight was\Njust about to reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,her grand master\Nplan for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I was kind\Nof wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,what we were going\Nto do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'd say we were\Nboth fairly interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you are. And I\Ndo have a plan, obviously,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but now's clearly not\Nthe time to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You should enjoy your party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ponyville Chronicle\Nwants to take our picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. You too,\NDiscord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,PSST. I see what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You already planned\Nthe perfect moment
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,during the party to make\Nthe grand announcement
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to everypony\Nabout your plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Brava, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to tell\NFluttershy and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:06:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight? Are you reading\Nduring a party again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no. She's\Nalready good at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She mastered this. She\Ntaught me about this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wild guess: something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, I'm a terrible mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I come up with\Na path for Starlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia had it\Nall figured out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I had years' worth\Nof friendship lessons
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,ready to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but when we were\Ncaptured by Chrysalis,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight took charge\Nand really stepped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think\Nfriendship lessons
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,are enough for\Nher anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have an overachieving\Nstudent? Sounds familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I had\Nto talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You of all ponies\Nwould know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you were me\Nand I was Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But for now, I need you to\Npretend you're you and I'm me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.27,0:07:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was your student\Nand you were in this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you... oh no. You\Nsent me to Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means, it's\Ntime for me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to send Starlight\NGlimmer away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is time for\NStarlight to go, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you can make\Nthat decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a difficult one, but your\Nheart knows what's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even as it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going\Nto send her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Too soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No. This is something\NI have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever Twilight's\Nplanning for Starlight
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to be\Nso exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Wonder why she didn't\Ntell any of us about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably because you're not as\Nclose as you think you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding. She wanted\Nit to be a big surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just between us,\Nshe's getting ready
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to make a big\Nannouncement!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:09:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeeee. That's so\Nexciting! And surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually you tell\Nyour party planner
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,about all your plans\Nfor your party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she definitely has one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean when has\NTwilight not had a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, gosh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I GOT IT!\NSince defeating Chrysalis,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight's given\Nthe changelings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,an opportunity to\Nrevolutionize their society.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can send her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If Starlight goes to\Nthe changeling hive,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,she can help them adjust\Nto their new way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, friendship one-oh-one:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorax and I are going to\Nshow you how to compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to have honeysuckle\Nnectar for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like a sandwich.\NOh, no. What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack! The winner\Ngets to choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,OR, Thorax and I can\Ntalk about it and come up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,with a solution that\Nworks for everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight. How do\Nyou feel about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,honeysuckle and peanut\Nbutter sandwiches?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, that sounds\Ndelicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Compromise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, this doesn't\Nseem like something
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight and\NThorax would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, this is Twilight's\Nfantasy, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no wrong\Nway to fantasize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight Glimmer is a most\Napt and perspicacious pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, definitely a\NTwilight fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This seems like a lovely\Npath for Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Changelings have\Nso much to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,about how to enjoy love\Nthrough friendships.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight would be busy\Nfor a very long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but her work there\Nwould be very rewarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Or dangerous. It would\Nonly take one Changeling
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to deviate from the pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Starlight Glimmer.\NWhat's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Cornicle?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,PFFFT! HA! What kind\Nof name is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wings are so\Num, see-through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I'm a pony.\NAre you like bugs or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is! Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, that probably\Nwon't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But it could. I can't\Njust send her off to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia-knows-where without\Nthinking it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. I was not aware\Nthat I was an expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,An appropriate one, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,for even I don't\Nknow the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a momentous\Ndecision.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You must consider all\Nthe possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rethink, rethink, rethink...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can send Starlight\Nto the Dragon Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She and Ember would\Ntotally hit it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Emberrrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Starliiiiight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You ready to do some\Ndeath-defying dragon stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, that doesn't sound anything
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,like Ember or Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what their\Ndynamic would be, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Freaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight will love it\Nin the dragon lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In her letters, Ember\Nsaid dragons do a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of fun things: The Feast\Nof Fires, the Dragon Bowl,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Clawchella...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight could be there\Nfor a really long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But then again, not\Nall dragons like ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,as much as Ember does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Twinkle Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's uh, Starlight Glimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Star-kle Light-star?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.42,0:13:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight Glimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.19,0:13:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah Whatever. You\Nwanna hang with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we diving into?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lava!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, this is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight's really\Ngood with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She could just stop\Nherself from falling
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,into a pit of lava.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What if she didn't\Nrealize it was happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You just never know, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need to think of\Nsomeplace safe to send her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Some place safe, some place\Nsafe. Some place safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I could send her to\Nthe Crystal Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to continue her magical\Nstudies with Sunburst!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunburst's knowledge of\Nmagic is only matched
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,by Starlight's abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.34,0:13:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it! Try placing your\Nhorn directly on the potion
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and picture the clock\Nyou wish to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They could challenge\Neach other into becoming
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the most talented unicorns\NEquestria's ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it! Quick,\Nwhat's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the study of\Nmagic is a lifelong pursuit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.51,0:14:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and Starlight could\Nbe there for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,especially once they\Nstart attempting
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the really complicated stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Three... two... one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What if they become\Ntoo ambitious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would have thought\Nto combine Starswirl's
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,apparition spell with\Nspatium flexibus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But what would\Nhappen if we added
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonambula's tempus\Nobjectus?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do it just right,\Nit should allow us
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to materialize an object\Nthat was lost in the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight! NOOOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy, Twilight.\NIt didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But it could.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't think I\Ncan send her anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you laughing at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\Nyou're laughing at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Twilight, I'm not.\NI'm laughing because
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the exact same\Nfears you're having.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Once upon a time there was\Na very bright young filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She was truly one\Nof my best students.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see what\Nyou're thinking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:15:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was constantly\Nsurprised and impressed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,with her discoveries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I noticed that her\Npursuit of academia
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,was preventing her from\Nreaching her full potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it was keeping\Nher isolated and alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Yes, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a decision to\Nmake. But it wasn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I could close the library
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,or throw a party in the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd have to talk to\Nthe other fillies then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I must send her away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew there was a special\Ngroup of fillies in Ponyville,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but I kept inventing\Nall kinds of reasons
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,why I shouldn't send you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What if she runs into a\Nmanticore? Or what if
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,she gets pulled into\NTartarus? Or worst of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,what if she doesn't\Nget along with anypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we supposed\Nto say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept you in Canterlot\Nlonger than I should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, I realized\Nall the anxiety I felt
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,was because I didn't\Nwant you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved having you\Nas a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You challenged me and\Ntaught me just as much
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.96,0:17:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,as I taught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I am embarrassed to admit\Nit, but I was afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,if you made friends, you\Nwouldn't need me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.81,0:17:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia,\Nthat is so not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I will always need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Starlight Glimmer\Nmight feel the same way
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,about you, if that is\Nwhat you're afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it is.\NJust a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it definitely\Nis. Like a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are after all\Nthese years, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We are living proof\Nthat letting someone
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,spread their wings doesn't\Nmean you no longer have
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a place in their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.63,0:17:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're still worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.34,0:18:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you can always make\Nher write you letters!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have let it slip\Nthat you'd be unveiling
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,your big plan for Starlight\Ntonight. Silly me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're all very excited to\Nhear what you've cooked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't coming up with\Na plan just now, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear. This could be\Npretty embarrassing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, thanks Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Anytime. I really do\Nlove being helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could have\Neverypony's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,As you all know, Starlight\NGlimmer has been my pupil
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,for a while now and I'd\Nhoped she'd be my pupil
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,for a long time yet to\Ncome, but it turns out
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that's just not meant to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight, you have proved\Nyourself to be a kind,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,loyal, strong, honest\Nand truly magical friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just looking around\Nthis room at
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,all the new friendships\Nyou've made,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.97,0:19:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know there's nothing\Nmore I need to teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have a second\Nreason to celebrate today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Three cheers for\NStarlight Glimmer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,on her "graduation" day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,EEE WHAT A GREAT SURPRISE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your future is in\Nyour own hooves now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. I was not expecting this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it. I was hoping you'd\Nsend her to my realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We could have been roomies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to not pick up what\NI was putting down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you wanna celebrate?\NGirls trip to Las Pegasus?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We can throw you a\Nchangeling Gorbfest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, it's more fun\Nthan it sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Or we could go cause\Na little mischief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a trick that'll turn\NCelestia's castle into cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's\Na gouda idea? Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the first\Nof many cheese jokes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,if we go down this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.34,0:20:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That all sounds\Nwonderful but um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a minute, would ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy, surprised, overwhelmed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, not that I'm not\Ngrateful but are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me, I've thought\Nlong and hard about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight, trust\Nme. You're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you\Ntalking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not ready to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good! Cuz I'm not\Nready for that either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. I got you\Nthis present.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.04,0:20:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was going to be a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,'congrats on getting a\Nmedal of honor present',
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but then I was afraid\Nit would have to be a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.18,0:20:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,'going away' present\Nbut now it's a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:20:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,'I couldn't be happier\Nyou're staying' present!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It fits perfectly over your\Ndresser. I know. I measured!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not know what\Ncomes next for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.77,0:21:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but whatever it is, I promise\NI'll always be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew!
